    {
      "name": "Cycling",
      "summary": "Underwhelming mechanic except in UR. Cycling doesn't justify reducing land counts below 16. Disparity exists between 1-mana (peak convenience but colored), 2-mana (moderate), and 3-mana cycles.",
      "performance": "Niche in UR only; otherwise mediocre.",
      "key_examples": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Vehicles",
      "summary": "A sad tragedy — despite the set's theme, vehicles are largely ineffective due to diminishing returns and insufficient pilot tokens. Quality vehicles (Voyager Glidecar, Earthrumbler) are playable; common vehicles are among the weakest cards in the format.",
      "performance": "Most vehicles are unplayable; a handful of premium options work.",
