  "general_tips": [
    "Budget for 3-5 vehicles maximum in most decks; artifact-heavy decks specifically require careful creature counts.",
    "Splashing works when bombs justify it; most color-fixing vehicles are undesirable standalone.",
    "Board stalls reaching natural decking are common — card advantage and mana sinks become crucial.",
    "Guardian Sunmare builds can use Lotusguard Disciple tutor capability and Flood the Engine synergy.",
    "Sab-Sunen (Luxa Embodied) has limited answers: Bounce Off, Flood the Engine, Trip Up, Possession Engine, and others.",
    "Don't dabble with Speed — either commit heavily or skip entirely.",
    "Remember to play Speed creatures before attacking to maximize triggers."
  ]
